少些抱怨，多些知足惜福。 11.人缘在很多时候，并不是一种资源，而是一种依靠，一种无形的力量。兄弟姐妹是你的后盾，在你困难的时候能给你最及时的帮忙，因此在处理人际关联时，个性是兄弟姐妹之间关联的时候，千万不能待人苛刻，更不能使留意眼，贪其中小便宜，睚眦必报之人最终会得到惩罚。 12未来总是充满荆棘，梦想总是遥不可及，如果生活为你设置了一些磨难，无须抱怨。即使做不到不抱怨，也应该尽量少一些抱怨，多一些积极的态度。抱怨就像搬起石头砸自己的脚，于人无益，于己不利，于事无补。"},"attached_info":"Cj8I+pLepd3Xh/w+EAMaCDY5ODYzMDg3INrmvokGMAA4lAFAIHIJNDg0MTE1MzE2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"59 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-7dd36ec48d5fe9b0679781a98af7c05c_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"33_1634396875.839401","card_id":"Q_488178347","target":{"id":488178347,"title":"教资从这会开始看来得及吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/488178347","type":"question","created":1632237424,"answer_count":146,"follower_count":204,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[21612,35835,108339,406727],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"用的中公的教材"},"attached_info":"Cj8I+pLepd3Xh/w+EAMaCDcwNzY1NjUxIPDup4oGMAA4zAFAIXIJNDg4MTc4MzQ3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"56 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-f89430d8916cbc34cc81d73376383d1e_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"34_1634396875.83983","card_id":"Q_492698478","target":{"id":492698478,"title":"如何评价doinb在s11的表现？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/492698478","type":"question","created":1634349161,"answer_count":50,"follower_count":60,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[18427,136272,154337,208238,389735],"comment_count":4,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4I+pLepd3Xh/w+EAMaCDcxNzcwMDI0IOngqIsGMAQ4PEAicgk0OTI2OTg0Nzh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"51 万热度","trend":0,"debut":